The '''Destruction of Shola''' was the massive cataclysm that destroyed the surface of [[Shola/Legends|Shola]], a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]]. All that eventually remained were the [[Shola Ruins|ruins]] on the surface and a mass of underground tunnels leading nearly to the core of the planet.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Empire at War]]''

